('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000300010000','Sneha Iyer','+91 99452 81360','Osaka','solo','2026-08-05','15:05','3D2N',1,'Everyone in Bengaluru warned a vegetarian would starve in Japan, and I am determined to come home and prove them gloriously wrong. I am obsessed with the Sengoku era — I want to stand inside Himeji''s keep and actually understand who fought there, not just photograph it. Please find me okonomiyaki and temple shojin cuisine that are genuinely vegetarian, not just lucky guesses.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,33500,33000,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0003","unit_order":1,"unit_total":4,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-05","trip_end_date":"2026-08-11","trip_total_duration":"7D6N","origin_country":"India","origin_city":"Bengaluru","ages":[31],"languages":["Tamil","English (fluent)","Hindi","Kannada (conversational)"],"occasion":"First solo trip abroad, booked the week she got promoted to lead engineer","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":33500,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":33000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":33000,"pace":"active","splurge_willingness":"one_two_splurges","dietary_restrictions":"vegetarian","mobility":"Fully mobile, loves long walking days and stair-heavy castle climbs","interests":["history","castles","food_dining","temples_shrines","local_culture"],"must_avoid":"Beef, pork and fish on the plate (strict vegetarian); also wary of places that just shrug when she asks about ingredients","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"mix","accommodation_preference":"Clean comfortable 4-star hotels with strong breakfasts; a machiya or castle-town inn for one night would be special"}'::jsonb),
