('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000500010000','Fatima Al-Mansoori','+971 56 482 9170','Tokyo','solo','2026-08-06','13:30','3D2N',1,'Abu Dhabi gave me skylines and heat; I am craving the opposite — still water, Mt Fuji reflected at dawn, raked gravel gardens in Kyoto. I want to wake before the crowds, photograph the mountain in silence, and be looked after well. Please make my halal needs clear to every kitchen in advance so I never have to interrogate a menu mid-meal; that quiet confidence is the whole point of this trip.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,37000,45000,
