('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000600010000','Seo-yeon Han','+82 10-3947-6028','Tokyo','couple','2026-08-02','14:00','3D2N',2,'Do-hyun and I almost broke up two years ago when his work swallowed us whole, and this is the trip where we get us back. I want one perfect evening soaking in a private Hakone onsen watching the steam rise, and a quiet dawn at a Kyoto temple before the crowds. Make it feel like the world slowed down for us.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,38000,26750,
