('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000800010000','Lukas Brandt','+49 151 24806739','Sapporo','couple','2026-08-05','14:15','3D2N',2,'We did Tokyo and Kyoto on our first trip and loved it, but we are mountain people at heart and felt boxed in by the cities. This time we want Hokkaido''s wide green summer: a hard hike up Mt Yotei if the weather holds, a soak afterwards, and a Yoichi whisky tasting for Lukas. Push our legs; we are happiest when we have earned the onsen.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,36500,24750,
