('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001000010000','Camille Tremblay','+1 514 803 7142','Fukuoka','couple','2026-08-09','14:45','3D2N',2,'Olivier took a posting in Calgary this year and we have basically lived on video calls; this trip is us pressing reset. We dreamed up Kyushu specifically because we wanted steam, quiet, and nobody else''s schedule. Please flag the shellfish allergy hard at every kaiseki dinner — Camille has been hospitalised before and it terrifies us both, but we do not want it to dominate the trip.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,35000,22500,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0010","unit_order":1,"unit_total":4,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-09","trip_end_date":"2026-08-15","trip_total_duration":"7D6N","origin_country":"Canada","origin_city":"Montreal","ages":[29,31],"languages":["French (native)","English (fluent)"],"occasion":"Reuniting for a real holiday after a year apart in a long-distance relationship","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":35000,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":45000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":22500,"pace":"moderate","splurge_willingness":"one_two_splurges","dietary_restrictions":"allergy (severe shellfish allergy — Camille)","mobility":"Both fully mobile; happy with relaxed onsen-town pacing and gentle walks, no demanding hikes wanted","interests":["onsen","food_dining","nature_hiking","local_culture","history"],"must_avoid":"Shellfish anywhere near Camille''s plate (severe allergy); also no jam-packed big-city itineraries, they want slow Kyushu onsen calm","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"planner_books_all","accommodation_preference":"Authentic onsen ryokan in Beppu and Yufuin with in-room or private baths and kaiseki dinners; this is the heart of the trip for them"}'::jsonb),
