('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001100010000','Lorenzo Ferretti','+39 333 482 7160','Tokyo','honeymoon','2026-08-08','14:10','3D2N',2,'We married in a tiny hillside chapel outside Florence in May and Japan has been Bianca''s dream since she was a girl folding paper cranes. We want the honeymoon to feel like a slow love letter, not a checklist: a private onsen where we can watch the mist lift off Mt Fuji, kaiseki by candlelight, and at least one quiet temple garden where it is just the two of us at opening time before the crowds. Please build in a romantic dinner for our one-month wedding anniversary on the 14th. Lorenzo is planning to give Bianca a letter that night, so a beautiful private setting matters more than anything.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,48000,46000,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0011","unit_order":1,"unit_total":4,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-08","trip_end_date":"2026-08-14","trip_total_duration":"7D6N","origin_country":"Italy","origin_city":"Florence","ages":[33,30],"languages":["Italian","English (fluent)","Spanish (conversational)"],"occasion":"honeymoon","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":48000,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":92000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":46000,"pace":"slow","splurge_willingness":"frequent","dietary_restrictions":"none","mobility":"Both fully mobile; happy with full walking days but want unhurried mornings to sleep in together","interests":["temples_shrines","onsen","food_dining","photography","gardens"],"must_avoid":"Packaged group bus tours and loud party districts; Bianca gets motion-sick on winding mountain bus roads so prefer trains where possible","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"planner_books_all","accommodation_preference":"One unforgettable ryokan night with a private open-air onsen and Mt Fuji or garden view; boutique design hotels with a king bed in the cities, never twin beds"}'::jsonb),
