('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001200010000','Wei Jie Tan','+65 9123 6748','Sapporo','honeymoon','2026-08-02','13:35','3D2N',2,'We chose Hokkaido in summer precisely because Singapore never gets cold — Rachel wants to wake up to crisp mountain air and a duvet, not air-con. We are outdoorsy newlyweds who would rather hike Mt Yotei and soak in a quiet onsen than shop, though Rachel has been dreaming of fresh Hokkaido uni and a romantic seafood dinner by the Otaru canal at dusk. One splurge night in a beautiful Niseko lodge with a private bath would make the trip; the rest we are happy to keep simple. This is the first time either of us has travelled for longer than a week, and the first as husband and wife.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,44000,40500,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0012","unit_order":1,"unit_total":3,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-02","trip_end_date":"2026-08-07","trip_total_duration":"6D5N","origin_country":"Singapore","origin_city":"Singapore","ages":[29,28],"languages":["English (native)","Mandarin","Malay (basic)"],"occasion":"honeymoon","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":44000,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":81000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":40500,"pace":"slow","splurge_willingness":"one_two_splurges","dietary_restrictions":"none","mobility":"Both fit and active; keen on day hikes and cycling, want at least one proper trail in the Niseko mountains","interests":["nature_hiking","onsen","food_dining","photography","local_culture"],"must_avoid":"Big crowded cities for too long and anything that feels like a generic city tour; we get plenty of skyscrapers at home and came to Japan for cool air and open landscape","previous_visits_japan":"been_before","booking_authority":"planner_recommends","accommodation_preference":"A design-led lodge or boutique ryokan in Niseko with mountain views and an onsen for the splurge night; comfortable modern hotels with a double bed in Sapporo and Otaru"}'::jsonb),
