('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001400010000','Mariana Ríos Beltrán','+52 55 3471 9028','Tokyo','family','2026-08-01','14:10','3D2N',4,'Our boy Diego has been obsessed with Pokemon and Studio Ghibli since he could talk, and getting him to the real Japan is the whole reason we saved for three years. Sofia, our daughter, is the foodie who wants to try everything on a stick. We want a trip where the kids look up from their screens and never want to leave — please weave in one or two moments that feel like pure movie magic for them.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,31000,26000,
