('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001500010000','Bram van der Heijden','+31 6 24817503','Sapporo','family','2026-08-02','13:50','3D2N',5,'We chose Hokkaido on purpose — we wanted the Japan that isn''t on every postcard, with lavender fields, cool summer air and trails the kids can run on. My wife Anouk teaches biology and is endlessly curious about the alpine flora up here. The teenagers grumble about everything at home but I want one trip where they''re too busy looking at mountains to be on their phones. Vegetarian meals for me and our youngest matter a lot.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,28500,22400,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0015","unit_order":1,"unit_total":3,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-02","trip_end_date":"2026-08-07","trip_total_duration":"6D5N","origin_country":"Netherlands","origin_city":"Utrecht","ages":[45,43,15,13,9],"languages":["Dutch","English (fluent)","German (basic)"],"occasion":"A big family adventure before our eldest starts exam years and the summers stop being ours","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":28500,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":112000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":22400,"pace":"moderate","splurge_willingness":"one_two_splurges","dietary_restrictions":"vegetarian","mobility":"Active outdoorsy family used to cycling and hiking; happy with full-day nature outings, the 9-year-old keeps up fine","interests":["nature_hiking","photography","local_culture","food_dining","onsen"],"must_avoid":"Big crowded shopping districts and theme-park queues; we came for Hokkaido''s open space, not city chaos. Two of us are vegetarian, so please confirm real options, not just a side salad","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"planner_recommends","accommodation_preference":"Spacious family-friendly lodges or pensions with room for five and good hiking access; a lakeside or mountain-view onsen stay would be the highlight"}'::jsonb),
