('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001600010000','Kanya Sirisopha','+66 81 472 6395','Fukuoka','family','2026-08-05','14:40','3D2N',4,'We adore hot springs back in Thailand but nothing compares to a Japanese onsen town, and Beppu and Yufuin have been on my list for years. My husband Somchai is the ramen hunter who will happily queue an hour for the right bowl. Our teenage daughter Ploy is quietly into photography and folklore, and our little one just wants to feed animals and splash in water. We want a soft, steam-and-greenery kind of trip, not a checklist.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,33000,24250,
