('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001700010000','Tania Hargreaves','+64 21 558 0937','Tokyo','family','2026-08-08','13:30','3D2N',3,'I''m raising two sixteen-year-old daughters on my own and this trip is my way of marking how far we''ve come together before they fly the nest. Aroha is the photographer who has storyboarded a whole shot list of Mt Fuji and Kyoto''s bamboo; Maia is the quieter one drawn to temples and old craft. One of the girls has a severe peanut allergy, so please confirm kitchens carefully — it genuinely keeps me up at night when we travel. I want them to feel trusted and a little bit grown-up on this one.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,30000,29667,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0017","unit_order":1,"unit_total":3,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-08","trip_end_date":"2026-08-13","trip_total_duration":"6D5N","origin_country":"New Zealand","origin_city":"Wellington","ages":[47,16,16],"languages":["English (native)","Maori (basic)"],"occasion":"A mother-and-twins trip — my last big adventure with the girls before they finish school and scatter","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":30000,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":89000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":29667,"pace":"moderate","splurge_willingness":"one_two_splurges","dietary_restrictions":"allergy","mobility":"All very mobile and energetic; happy with long walking days and a Mt Fuji-area hike, no concerns","interests":["photography","temples_shrines","nature_hiking","art_museums","local_culture"],"must_avoid":"Severe peanut allergy for one twin — this is non-negotiable and must be flagged at every restaurant. Otherwise avoid heavily packaged big-group tours; the girls want it to feel independent","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"planner_books_all","accommodation_preference":"A triple room or family room in characterful boutique hotels; one ryokan night near Mt Fuji with a lake or mountain view would mean everything for the photos"}'::jsonb),
