('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001800010000','Ramon Bautista','+63 917 482 6035','Tokyo','group','2026-08-03','14:00','3D2N',4,'We grew up watching anime dubbed in Tagalog on lazy Sunday afternoons and swore we''d see the real thing one day. This is that day. We want one unforgettable late-night ramen-and-beers session where we toast to still being friends after all these years, and a quiet onsen soak to nurse the next morning. Don''t over-schedule us — let us breathe.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,34500,24500,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0018","unit_order":1,"unit_total":4,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-03","trip_end_date":"2026-08-09","trip_total_duration":"7D6N","origin_country":"Philippines","origin_city":"Manila","ages":[34,33,35,32],"languages":["Filipino","English (fluent)"],"occasion":"Four college barkada finally cashing in a promise made at graduation a decade ago to do Japan together before kids and mortgages made it impossible","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":34500,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":98000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":24500,"pace":"active","splurge_willingness":"one_two_splurges","dietary_restrictions":"none","mobility":"All four fully mobile, used to long humid walking days back home; happy with moderate hill climbs and plenty of stairs at shrines","interests":["temples_shrines","ramen_streetfood","onsen","photography","nightlife"],"must_avoid":"Cookie-cutter big bus tours and anything that herds us around on a tight leash; we want pockets of free time to eat and wander on our own","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"planner_recommends","accommodation_preference":"One large shared apartment or connecting twin rooms per stop so the four of us stay together and can hang out late; one night in a proper onsen ryokan with private bath as the splurge"}'::jsonb),
